  <description><![CDATA[<p>Split between two buildings, the <a data-udi="umb://document/e7efe5a844524bb0a32e79486bc81440" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e7efe5a844524bb0a32e79486bc81440}" title="Montsoleil Terrasses d'Eos Apartments">Terrasses d'Eos</a> and the Terrasses d'Helios apartments have been beautifully designed and built in a Savoyard style, and with a great location in Flaine you are only a short distance from the lifts and resort centre.</p>
<h2>Ski in, ski out</h2>
<p>Surrounded by peaceful pine forests in the Montsoleil area, the residence has a great location slightly set back from the hustle and bustle of the centre of Flaine. The apartments are in a ski in/ski out location giving you convenient access to the slopes each day, plus the ski school also conveniently meets at the residence. The centre of the resort is a five minute walk, where you can find a range of shops, bars and restaurants to keep you occupied when you are not on the slopes.</p>
<h2>Savoyard style</h2>
<p>The Montsoleil Terrasses d'Helios Apartments offer luxury apartments in Flaine, each apartment has been furnished to a high standard in a traditional Savoyard style blending wood and stone to create a warm and welcoming atmosphere. You have all the amenities needed for a relaxing stay in the mountains, the fully equipped kitchen means you can whip up tasty meals or you can treat yourself to a meal in the on site restaurant serving delicious French dishes, which is open to both the public and residents.</p>
<h2>Unwind and relax</h2>
<p>After a day of exploring the slopes, the residence has great facilities available for it's guests. With large windows overlooking the Grand Massif, the wellness area is the perfect place to relax. Take a dip in the indoor swimming pool,  unwind and relax in the hammam or sauna, alternatively you can soak away any aches and pains in the hot tub. There is also the <span>deep nature spa, and for a little extra cost, you can treat yourself to a massage or beauty treatment. If you are not worn out by a day on the slopes, stay in shape at the fitness studio which has a range of equipment available. </span></p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
