  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>One bedroom apartments</strong> can sleep two to four people and are around 35m². The apartments have a twin bedroom and a living room with double sofa bed. </p>
<p><strong>Two bedroom apartments</strong> can sleep three to six people and are around 50m². The apartments have one double bedroom, one twin bedroom and a living room with double sofa bed.</p>
<p><strong>Superior two bedroom apartments with mountain views</strong> can sleep three to six people and are around 60m². The apartments have one twin bedroom, one double bedroom and a larger living room with double sofa bed.</p>
<p>All rooms can take a cot.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Apartment facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Kitchenette equipped with kettle, tea and coffee making facilities including coffee machine and electric kettle, toaster, dish washer, microwave, oven, hobs, fridge</li>
